THE DOG WHO REFUSED TO LEAVE

00:00:13.180 --> 00:00:15.750
HIS OWNER'S SIDE AFTER HE DIED

00:00:15.750 --> 00:00:16.050
IS SHOWING STRONG SIDES OF

00:00:16.050 --> 00:00:16.880
GRIEF.

